high_descs: Walk forward, then turn left and walk over to the black shelf on the wall.
Pick up the set of keys off of the black shelf.
Walk over to the coffee table behind you.
Put the set of keys on the white plate that is on the coffee table.
Pick up the white plate with the keys on it off of the coffee table.
Turn right and walk towards the wall, then turn right and walk up to the black bench.
Put the white plate with the keys on it on the right side of the black bench.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with some keys on it on a bench.

high_descs: Turn to the left and find the shelf on the wall.
Pick up the keys from the shelf on the wall.
Carry the keys and turn to the right and then right again to face the coffee table.
Place the keys on the plate, to the left side of the coffee table.
Pick up the plate from the coffee table.
Carry the plate and turn to the right. Turn right again to find the bench on the floor.
Place the plate and keys on the bench, to the right side.
anns.task_desc: Move a plate and keys to a bench.

high_descs: Turn left and walk forward to face the shelves on the wall.
Pick up the keys on the shelf on the wall.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the living room table.
Place the keys on the plate on the living room table.
Pick up the plate with the keys on it on the living room table.
Turn around and step forward to face the platform on the floor.
Set the plate with keys on it on the platform on the floor.
anns.task_desc: To put keys on a plate and place them on a platform next to an empty box.
